                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7498,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Kitsune Saiguu",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "The Kakushigami of the bake-danuki was Kitsune Saiguu's friend and rival. When the",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 7089,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/10/12/237301566/93cd2bc9b90c8b87b1f8cbdbe95b4b9d_1090730713764694732.png",
                      "menu_id": 20,
                      "name": "Катаклизм в Каэнри'ах",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "started 500 years ago, she offered him to play hide-and-seek so he wouldn't be harmed. However, she didn't come back and died from the Abyssal corruption. Ioroi still doesn't his friend died.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7501,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Kamuna Harunosuke",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "When Kitsune Saiguu did not return, Ioroi began to wreak havoc around himself in order to lure his friend out. He stole the ward needed to purify the Sacred Sakura, thinking it was an ordinary comb. For this, the Shogun sent Kamuna Harunosuke to deal with Ioroi, who turned the bake-danuki king and the other tanuki of the forest into stone.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
